graph TD
    Dev["👨‍💻 Developer"] -->|git push| GitHub["🐙 GitHub Repository"]
    
    GitHub -->|Trigger Webhook| Action["⚙️ GitHub Action<br/>.github/workflows"]
    
    Action -->|Checkout Code| Checkout["📥 Checkout Repository<br/>Clone latest code"]
    
    Checkout -->|Install Deps| Install["📦 Install Dependencies<br/>pip install -r requirements.txt"]
    
    Install -->|Run Tests| Test["✅ Run Tests<br/>pytest"]
    
    Test -->|Tests Pass| Build["🔨 Build Docker Image<br/>docker build"]
    
    Build -->|Tag Image| Tag["🏷️ Tag Image<br/>medical-chatbot:latest"]
    
    Tag -->|Push to Registry| ECR["📦 AWS ECR<br/>Elastic Container Registry"]
    
    ECR -->|Update Service| Deploy["🚀 Deploy to EC2<br/>Stop old container<br/>Start new container"]
    
    Deploy -->|Verify Health| HealthCheck["❤️ Health Check<br/>Test endpoints"]
    
    HealthCheck -->|Success| Production["✅ Production<br/>Live on AWS"]
    
    Test -->|Tests Fail| Failure["❌ Build Failed<br/>Notify Developer"]
    
    Failure -->|Alert| Slack["📢 Slack Notification<br/>Deployment failed"]
    
    Production -->|Live| Users["👥 Users<br/>Access Chatbot"]
    
    style Dev fill:#e8f5e9
    style GitHub fill:#000000,color:#fff
    style Action fill:#fff3e0
    style Build fill:#f3e5f5
    style ECR fill:#e3f2fd
    style Deploy fill:#fff9c4
    style Production fill:#c8e6c9
    style Users fill:#c8e6c9